    • connection

      public HttpURLConnection connection(String url, Object... param) throws IOException
      A shorthand method for creating usable https connections, please note that this method opens the connection for you beforehand, it's your job though to disconnect it once you no longer need the connection
      Parameters:
      url - The target url
      param - Optional parameters to be included in the url
      Returns:
      A usable connection.
      Throws:
      IOException - when the connection failed to create
